CHANGES
============================================================================

Release 0.2.3 (2010-02-05)
--------------------------

[Bugfixes]

  * feedreader, pastebin: Catch errors while fetching page.


Release 0.2.2 (2010-02-02)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * Make SleekXMPP plugins configurable.

  * Replace ElementTree by cElementTree.

  * chatbot, pastebin plugins: make configuration more simple.

[Bugfixes]

  * chatbot plugin: add 'log' extension for debug logs.


Release 0.2.1 (2010-01-31)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * New plugins: antispam.

[Bugfixes]

  * chatbot plugin: !shut not working.

  * feedreader plugin: autosanitaze database.


Release 0.2 (2010-01-28)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * New plugins: pastebin.

  * Port the code to Python 3.1.

  * A lot of code refactoring.


Release 0.1 (2009-08-20)
--------------------------

[Enhancements]

  * Initial set of plugins.